      "settings": {
        "intro_title": "The Only Treatment is Prevention.",
        "intro_text": "<p>Unlike most bodily injuries we humans can suffer, there’s really no treatment for a Traumatic Brain Injury (TBI). The focus has to be on prevention. That’s why each Hardknock helmet is designed with innovative Nuro technology to mitigate force from both direct impact and rotational torque. With unmatched fit and comfort, so workers actually want to wear it. By integrating Hardknock helmets into workplace safety programs, employers help their workers reduce the risk and incidence of TBI, and feel more secure.</p>",
        "intro_image": "shopify://shop_images/tbi-intro-helmet.png"
      }
